General.Name: MRG Metals Ltd
General.Description: MRG Metals Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration and development of heavy mineral sands in Mozambique. The company holds interests in Heavy Mineral Sands projects comprising 2 licenses the Corridor Central and Corridor South covering and area of 387 square kilometers; the Linhuane Project that consists of 113 square kilometers; and the Marao and Marruca projects comprising approximately 385 square kilometers located in Mozambique. MRG Metals Ltd was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Ballarat, Australia.
